<section id="contacto" class="section contacto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-header">
      <p class="section-label">Contacto</p>
      <h2 class="section-title">
        ¿Tenés un lugar<br />para mí en tu <span class="highlight">equipo?</span
        >
      </h2>
      <hr class="divider" />
      <p class="contact-intro">
        Estoy disponible para incorporarme de manera flexible — ya sea part-time
        o cubriendo francos. Escribime y lo charlamos.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-cards">
      <a href="mailto:lunafreelancerr@gmail.com" class="contact-card">
        <div class="card-icon mail-icon">✉</div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-label mono">Email</span>
          <span class="card-value">lunafreelancerr@gmail.com</span>
          <span class="card-action">Escribime →</span>
        </div>
      </a>

      <a
        href="https://wa.me/5491136081560"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener"
        class="contact-card"
      >
        <div class="card-icon wsp-icon">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="currentColor" width="26" height="26">
            <path
              d="M17.472 14.382c-.297-.149-1.758-.867-2.03-.967-.273-.099-.471-.148-.67.15-.197.297-.767.966-.94 1.164-.173.199-.347.223-.644.075-.297-.15-1.255-.463-2.39-1.475-.883-.788-1.48-1.761-1.653-2.059-.173-.297-.018-.458.13-.606.134-.133.298-.347.446-.52.149-.174.198-.298.298-.497.099-.198.05-.371-.025-.52-.075-.149-.669-1.612-.916-2.207-.242-.579-.487-.5-.669-.51-.173-.008-.371-.01-.57-.01-.198 0-.52.074-.792.372-.272.297-1.04 1.016-1.04 2.479 0 1.462 1.065 2.875 1.213 3.074.149.198 2.096 3.2 5.077 4.487.709.306 1.262.489 1.694.625.712.227 1.36.195 1.871.118.571-.085 1.758-.719 2.006-1.413.248-.694.248-1.289.173-1.413-.074-.124-.272-.198-.57-.347m-5.421 7.403h-.004a9.87 9.87 0 01-5.031-1.378l-.361-.214-3.741.982.998-3.648-.235-.374a9.86 9.86 0 01-1.51-5.26c.001-5.45 4.436-9.884 9.888-9.884 2.64 0 5.122 1.03 6.988 2.898a9.825 9.825 0 012.893 6.994c-.003 5.45-4.437 9.884-9.885 9.884m8.413-18.297A11.815 11.815 0 0012.05 0C5.495 0 .16 5.335.157 11.892c0 2.096.547 4.142 1.588 5.945L.057 24l6.305-1.654a11.882 11.882 0 005.683 1.448h.005c6.554 0 11.89-5.335 11.893-11.893a11.821 11.821 0 00-3.48-8.413z"
            ></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="card-content">
          <span class="card-label mono">WhatsApp</span>
          <span class="card-value">+54 9 11 3608-1560</span>
          <span class="card-action">Mandame un mensaje →</span>
        </div>
      </a>
    </div>

    <div class="dev-note">
      <span class="neon-tag">💻 ¿También necesitás una web?</span>
      <p>
        Hago sitios web como freelance. Si tu negocio necesita presencia online,
        también podemos trabajarlo juntos.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contacto {
    background: var(--cream);
  }

  .contact-header {
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-bottom: 3rem;
  }

  .contact-intro {
    color: var(--muted);
    font-size: 1rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .contact-cards {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }

  .contact-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1.5rem;
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--sand);
    transition:
      border-color 0.2s,
      transform 0.2s,
      box-shadow 0.2s;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .contact-card:hover {
    border-color: var(--amber);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
    box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(200, 129, 58, 0.12);
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 56px;
    height: 56px;
    border-radius: 14px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .mail-icon {
    background: var(--amber);
    color: white;
  }
  .wsp-icon {
    background: #25d366;
    color: white;
  }

  .card-content {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 3px;
  }

  .card-label {
    font-size: 0.68rem;
    color: var(--muted);
    letter-spacing: 0.12em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  .card-value {
    font-size: 1rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--bark);
  }

  .card-action {
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--amber);
    margin-top: 4px;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .dev-note {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    background: var(--warm-dark);
    border-radius: 14px;
    padding: 1.4rem 1.8rem;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  .dev-note p {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: #a8987e;
    line-height: 1.65;
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 200px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .contact-cards {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
    .contact-card {
      padding: 1.5rem;
    }
    .card-value {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      word-break: break-all;
    }
    .dev-note {
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 0.75rem;
    }
  }
</style>
